on Martin DB3]]\n|-\n| 1953\n| Goodwood International  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/race/Goodwood-1953-09-26-6766.html|title=Goodwood International [S+1.5] 1953 - Racing Sports Cars|website=www.racingsportscars.com|accessdate=8 December 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#ffffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|H. W. Motors]]\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|HWM-Jaguar]]\n|-\n| \n| [[1953 12 Hours of Sebring|Grand Prix, 12 Hours of Sebring]]  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/results/Sebring-1953-03-08.html|title=Sebring 12 Hours 1953 - Race Results - Racing Sports Cars|website=www.racingsportscars.com|accessdate=8 December 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| 2nd\n| [[Aston Martin|Aston Martin Ltd.]]\n| [[Aston Martin DB3]]\n|-\n| 1954\n| Silverstone International  <ref name=\"racingsportscars.com\"/>\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| 2nd\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|H. W. Motors]]\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|HWM-Jaguar]]\n|-\n| \n| Hedemoraloppet  <ref name=\"racingsportscars.com\"/>\n| style=\"background:#dfdfdf;\"| 2nd\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|H. W. Motors]]\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|HWM-Jaguar]]\n|-\n| \n| Goodwood International  <ref name=\"racingsportscars.com\"/>\n| style=\"background:#ffdf9f;\"| 3rd\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|H. W. Motors]]\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|HWM-Jaguar]]\n|-\n| 1955\n| AMOC USAF Trophy  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/race/Oulton_Park-1955-09-17-11996.html|title=National Oulton Park [Sports Unlimited] 1955 - Racing Sports Cars|website=www.racingsportscars.com|accessdate=8 December 2017}}</ref>\n| style=\"background:#ffffbf;\"| '''1st'''\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|H. W. Motors]]\n| [[Hersham and Walton Motors|HWM-Jaguar]]\n|-\n| \n| BM Trophy  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.racingsportscars.com/race/Goodwood-1955-09-24-12143.html|title=BARC Goodwood [S3.5] 1955 - Racing Sports Cars|website=www.racingsportscars.com|accessdate=